message.text:
BEEP BEEP!! ANDITO NA ANG CramBayan MGA SUKI.  🚛

Ano pang inaantay niyo? Aba naman sugod na! At para sa mga takot maubusan kung ako sainyo mag pa reserve na kayo. 

📍RMC STOR LERMA ST. (beside FEU MNL) 
⏰: 9:00am to 3:00pm
———————————————
NEW PRODUCTS: 

• 🥟🍫 5PCS CHOCO XLB w/ Seasalt Cream ₱120 
•🥭THAI MANGO STICKY RICE ₱120 
•🍗🥗 CHICKEN CAESAR SALAD W/ SAUCE ₱150 

————————————————————————

Rice Meals:

•🍗🍚 CHICKEN CORDON BLEU W/ Tartar Sauce & Rice ₱120 

•🐣👑 CHICKEN ALA KING ₱120 

•🥓🍳BACSILOG W/ Cheese Sauce ₱120

• 🐮🧄GARLIC PEPPER BEEF w/ Rice ₱120 (no pork)

•🧆🍟 ULTIMATE BURGER STEAK w/ Fries & Rice ₱120 (no pork)

————————————————————————
Pastas: 

•🍝 CREAMY SHRIMP PESTO PASTA w/ 2pcs Pesto Bread (no pork) ₱150

•🍝CHEESY BEEF LASAGNA w/  2pcs Garlic Pesto Bread (no pork!!!) ₱150

•🍝 CREAMY CARBONARA w/ Chicken Cordon Bleu ₱150 

•🍝 MAC N CHEESE W/ Chicken Tenders (honey mustard, garlic parmersan, spicy bbq) ₱150 

-PM ME FOR RESERVATION/ORDERS 🫶🏻
-MOP: GCASH OR CASH
